data.description: This impeccably maintained open concept home surpasses the charm of new homes. Illuminated by an abundance of natural light, it exudes elegance w/many upgrades. Revel in the new LVP throughout, a fresh interior palette, contemporary light fixtures, new toilets & a new AC. The expansive kitchen is a culinary delight, showcasing ss appliances, breakfast bar, & a spacious pantry are seamlessly connected to living room featuring a charming fireplace an ideal space for relaxation & entertainment. Escape to the serene primary suite, complete w/a walk-in shower, a luxurious soaking tub, & a generously sized walk-in closet. The fully fenced backyard beckons w/a covered patio, creating a perfect setting for gatherings & outdoor enjoyment w/a storage shed & gardening area. Don't miss out on this meticulous home that balances functionality & style, offering a retreat-like atmosphere w/easy access to shopping & freeways. ONLY eligible VA members can seize the ASSUMABLE RATE AT 2.875%.
